title: 197: Early Preseason Rookie Standouts
itunes:title: 197: Early Preseason Rookie Standouts
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down the fallout from the big trades involving the Eagles, Bills and Rams. The guys also review what has transpired so far this preseason including rookie quarterbacks DeShone Kizer, Deshaun Watson and Mitchell Trubisky shining early.
